1. *Provalio* sam u kuću kroz prozor. (I broke into the house through the window.)
2. Nisam mogao da *provalim* šta je ona htela da kaže. (I couldn't figure out what she meant.)
3. Oni su *provalili* u banku i ukrali novac. (They broke into the bank and stole money.)
4. Ne želim da *provaljujem* tajnu. (I don't want to reveal the secret.)
5. Kada sam čuo vic, nisam se mogao suzdržati i *provalio* sam u smeh. (When I heard the joke, I couldn't help it and burst out laughing.)
6. Većina ljudi misli da su lopovi samo oni koji *provaljuju* u kuće. (Most people think that thieves are only those who break into houses.)
7. On je stalno *provaljivao* fore i činio nas smejati. (He constantly cracked jokes and made us laugh.)
8. Kada sam mu rekao tu vest, on je *provalio* u suze. (When I told him the news, he burst into tears.)